    <!-- Dialog -->
    <string name="carbonfibers_dialog_title">Help us help you!</string>
    <string name="carbonfibers_dialog_message">Unfortunately, we are not wizards!\n\nSo, if you find a bug with any setting in CarbonFibers, please open up a ticket on Jira or contact a Carbon developer with the following.\n\n1. Blame kwoktopus\n2. Logcat and/or last_kmsg\n3. Kernel and mods used\n4. Useful information (subjective)\n\nIf you fail to report something with the above information, do not expect things to be fixed. Remember, we are not as perfect as Patrick, so we do miss things occasionally.</string>
    <string name="carbonfibers_dialog_toast">READ THE WHOLE THING!</string>

